{
  "_comment": "Rosetta decision-library config. This file is OPTIONAL — delete it and the rosetta defaults below apply. Copy it into any project's decisions/ root and edit to use your team's own record types, directories, numbering, statuses, and templates. Parsed by scripts/decisions.py (pure stdlib JSON, no PyYAML).",
